This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Include all codes defined in http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/operation-outcome
  • Import all the codes that are contained in https://awatson.pages.mitre.org/hello-implementation-guide/StructureDefinition-DeqmOperationOutcomeCodeSystem.html
